27.5773, 328.1295, 328.5372, 328.9573, 328.1828, 327.8589, 328.4227, 328.1986, 327.4348, 328.375, 326.5829, 326.0746, 326.0638, 326.1117, 326.6042, 326.9396, 325.8127, 326.0654, 326.8214, 326.2783, 326.1018, 325.9464, 326.5898, 326.3741, 325.5786, 325.0831, 324.8726, 325.2988, 325.3944, 326.1899, 326.834, 327.446, 327.9747, 329.1127, 328.3478, 328.3249, 329.3475, 328.0697, 327.8997, 327.1886, 326.92, 327.6873, 326.8463, 326.2812, 326.4697, 327.9972, 325.7934, 326.3526, 325.8279, 326.0156, 326.46, 327.0848, 327.6778, 327.5881, 328.3409, 328.9136, 329.7711, 330.536, 331.1963, 330.4906, 330.1894, 329.7062, 329.2783, 328.4172, 328.3861, 328.7292, 328.9699, 327.9452, 327.4419, 327.8208, 327.3564, 328.1504, 328.0462, 327.4926, 327.2843, 328.3471, 327.9062, 327.7149, 327.886, 326.6859, 325.5103, 325.9834, 325.932, 325.1001, 324.4862, 325.4544, 326.3119, 325.8737, 325.4636, 326.208, 326.2871, 326.6393, 326.4301, 325.8321, 324.5616, 324.5216, 324.1405, 323.7921, 324.0475, 324.1989, 323.3639, 324.7578, 324.2029, 324.37, 324.1388, 324.6453, 324.7082, 324.8211, 324.8608, 324.8178, 326.1531, 326.519, 326.159, 326.7052, 326.5246, 325.469, 325.4028, 326.8963, 326.9167, 326.5879, 327.5945, 328.3948, 326.5743, 325.5367, 323.9323, 323.6108, 323.8654, 322.1463, 322.1927, 322.6833, 322.9321, 322.6499, 322.7303, 322.4793, 322.3168, 321.6373, 322.1177, 321.9022, 322.1924, 322.5582, 323.5651, 322.386, 322.0407, 322.2678, 322.511, 322.9991, 322.2502, 323.5637, 322.8358, 322.9864, 324.1272, 324.0129, 325.2091, 325.0786, 326.5544, 325.2142, 325.5329, 325.2194, 324.6121, 323.5056, 324.7089, 323.9083, 323.8436, 324.3316, 325.207, 325.1554, 324.5705, 324.8844, 324.5953, 325.0571, 325.3625, 324.7728, 324.425, 324.4489, 324.9977, 325.8972, 327.454, 326.4309, 327.1256, 327.2109, 330.1049, 328.9079, 330.3506, 331.0143, 331.2813, 330.918, 330.2513, 329.9359, 332.6092, 332.6256, 331.0642, 329.8534, 329.3181, 330.2872, 329.8923, 329.7976, 330.0968, 329.6605, 330.1928, 330.4939, 331.3486, 330.2641, 331.2154, 331.4178, 331.0284, 330.1158, 329.1927, 329.286, 328.0947, 328.2011, 329.5631, 329.8338, 329.5557, 329.6428, 329.7757, 330.0379, 330.8815, 331.1188, 330.2303, 330.9463], "summary_html": "<h1>库存水平时序偏离度因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 2.21)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本因子利用商品期货多头库存（inventory_lp）的时序偏离度构建截面多空信号。核心逻辑是：当某品种的库存水平显著偏离其历史均值（以滚动Z-score衡量），市场对该品种的供需定价可能存在偏差。因子在截面上对所有品种的Z-score进行百分位排名，做多库存异常偏高的品种、做空库存异常偏低的品种。</p>\n<p>该因子表现极为稳健：样本内Sharpe 2.21，两个半样本分别为2.79和2.54，时序IC正向品种占比86%，与现有因子库最大相关仅0.40，是一个独立且强劲的基本面截面因子。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>2.08</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>7.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-3.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.12</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2480</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>2.21</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.12</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>2.28 / 2.17</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.49</span></td><td>0.97</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.94</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.05</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.73</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.68</span></td><td>1.12</td><td>1.56</td><td>1.86</td><td>0.83</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.21</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 1 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 1 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>56</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2482</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>97.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>43.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{inventory\\_lp}_{i,t} - \\mu_{i}(W)}{\\sigma_{i}(W)}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\mu_{i}(W)</span> 和 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{i}(W)</span> 分别为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 的 <span class=\"math-tex\">W</span> 日滚动均值和标准差。</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{percentile\\_rank}_{cs}(z_{i,t})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = (\\text{rank}_{i,t} - 0.5) \\times 2 \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{direction}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{signal}_{i,t}}{\\sum_j |\\text{signal}_{j,t}|}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\text{direction}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\text{vol\\_target}}{\\hat{\\sigma}^{\\text{realized}}_{i,t} \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 2.00)</strong>：初始实现，覆盖基准逻辑（inventory_lp zscore -&gt; rank -&gt; continuous signal -&gt; L1 normalize -&gt; vol_target_scale）。参数网格覆盖 zs_window={126,180,252,504}、hold_days={1,5,10,20}、vol_target={0.10,0.15,0.20}，以及 inventory_sp 和 lp+sp 组合变体。意外发现 zs=126（半年窗口）优于基准的 zs=252，inv_lp_zs126_h5_raw 达到 Sharpe 2.00。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 1.94)</strong>：扩展参数空间（加入 zs=63/90），添加 sym_rolling_ic_gate 过滤弱品种，测试 inventory_ln 字段。R2 最优变体 inv_combo_zs126_h5_raw (Sharpe 1.94) 略低于 R1，但验证了信号在不同库存字段间的稳健性。IC-gate 变体与非 gate 变体持平，说明信号在大多数品种上均有效（77% 品种 IC&gt;0）。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 2.21)</strong>：关键突破。在 zs=100/126/150 范围内做细粒度参数网格，同时覆盖 vol_target={0.10,0.15,0.20} 和 hold_days={1,5}。发现低 vol_target (0.10) 配合 hold=1 显著提升 Sharpe（从 2.00 到 2.21），原因是更保守的波动率目标降低了噪声品种的仓位暴露。新增 inventory_sn (Sharpe 1.64) 和 inventory_21 (Sharpe -0.41) 的对比确认了 inventory_lp 是最佳字段。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>主要字段</strong>: inventory_lp（多头库存，非空率约36%总体，近年&gt;90%）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（56个有库存数据）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每日换仓或5日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 基本面数据（inventory_lp）存在历史NaN，早期品种覆盖率较低\n<p>- 低 vol_target (0.10) 导致绝对收益偏低（年化 4.5%），但风险调整后表现优异 - inventory_21 字段信号为负，不适合此逻辑</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.43s</li>\n</ul>"}